#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag3.5:4.1"
msgid "3.5. Mātaṅgaputtattheragāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc231"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts231"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.5:5.1"
msgid "“Atisītaṃ atiuṇhaṃ,"
msgstr "“It’s too cold, too hot,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:5.2"
msgid "atisāyamidaṃ ahu;"
msgstr "Too late,” they say."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:5.3"
msgid "Iti vissaṭṭhakammante,"
msgstr "Those who neglect their work like this—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:5.4"
msgid "khaṇā accenti māṇave."
msgstr "Opportunities pass them by."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc232"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts232"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.5:6.1"
msgid "Yo ca sītañca uṇhañca,"
msgstr "But one who considers hot and cold"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:6.2"
msgid "tiṇā bhiyyo na maññati;"
msgstr "To be nothing more than a blade of grass;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:6.3"
msgid "Karaṃ purisakiccāni,"
msgstr "He does his manly duty,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:6.4"
msgid "so sukhā na vihāyati."
msgstr "And his happiness never fails."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc233"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts233"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.5:7.1"
msgid "Dabbaṃ kusaṃ poṭakilaṃ,"
msgstr "With my chest I’ll thrust aside"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:7.2"
msgid "usīraṃ muñjapabbajaṃ;"
msgstr "The grasses, vines, and creepers, "

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:7.3"
msgid "Urasā <span class=\"var\" title=\"panudahissāmi (s2, s3, pts1)\" id=\"note156\">panudissāmi</span>,"
msgstr "And devote myself to seclusion."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.5:7.4"
msgid "vivekamanubrūhayan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
